summary: AN ORDINANCE transferring jurisdiction over certain City (general municipal purposes) property in the Replat of Blocks 44 to 53 inclusive Mercer's 2nd Addition to North Seattle to the Engineering Department for street purposes (5th Avenue North), and providing for reimbursement of the Cumulative Reserve Fund by a transfer of funds from an appropriation heretofore made by Ordinance 100183 from the Arterial City Street Fund in connection with the widening of 5th Avenue North.
